  "texts": [
    "Our internet search period ended in November, 2023.",
    "Selection CriteriaTools/algorithms that provided a free trial period were preferred.",
    "Further, among the tools requiring a subscription, those catering to individual researchers and those that could be bought online were preferred.",
    "We compared the various features of these tools and prepared a comprehensive list of these tools and their distinguishing features.",
    "The major tools/algorithms in certain sections have been compared and contrasts have been provided in tabulated forms."
  ]
}